p409
aa(lp410
VWe will be meeting in Paris at the end of this year,
p411
aVbut until we can think of this as a global phenomenon,
p412
aVbecause we create it, individually, as nations,
p413
aVbut it affects everybody else,
p414
aVand yet, we refuse to do anything about it,
p415
aVand we deal with it as a national problem,
p416
aVwhich it is not \u2014 it is a global issue,
p417
aVand it's got to be dealt with collectively.
p418
aa(lp419
VCA: People are incredibly bad at responding to graphs and numbers,
